{"tid":1795101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今世人真係過得好唔開心","createTime":"2019-12-23T15:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T18:12:33.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d96d82e5c5b73adc9fdc86fe8ec499ea0487571f","tid":1795101,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:29:12.000Z","msg":"不過有乜法子<br />\n相比以前<br />\n而家其實已經好少少<br />\n稱唔上開心<br />\n但已經冇咁唔開心<br />\n識處理<br />\n識麻醉自己<br />\n識逃避<br />\n以前同而家最大分別<br />\n係以前仲幻想自己終有一日開心返<br />\n好努力咁去做d咩夾硬令自己開心<br />\n連自己都以為自己開心<br />\n但原來開心分兩種<br />\n一種係客觀<br />\n一種係主觀<br />\n主觀既開心<br />\n其實即係自欺欺人<br />\n訓街邊d乞兒話自己開心<br />\n你信唔信<br />\n做人真係好on9<br />\non9到震<br />\n又可以點<br />\n根本連開心依樣野都係on9"},{"pid":"8e71da6dbee4b3ca51a25490bfef9dc81e43269c","tid":1795101,"uid":88940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/xmasevehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehk&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=70d38466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/xmasevehk</a><br />\n唔好意思借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟攬炒！香港人果七千萬比人搞啊！佢老母仲OT成九億<br />\n1224<br />\n1225<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[行動] [推上熱門] 我宣佈 聽日平安夜攬炒正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794689</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f4e5b72927e686da3abffceab401328c08ac6540","tid":1795101,"uid":120588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"主觀開心幾好<br />\n找到自己開心的方法 很好啊<br />\n唔好開心一陣又去否定佢 唔好常比較"},{"pid":"66dd8476d51a42a49e8b465b00d440208f3457d2","tid":1795101,"uid":225733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"如果有人話自己日日都過得好開心一定係假<br />\n我覺得有錢人都唔開心"}]}